{
  "stem": "7094.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was never invited to-- to a Polish home or my friends.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We met in school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, of course, the test came during the war, which you just realize how deeply rooted.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was very painful to accept, that people you went to school and you play in the foreground, you know, enjoyed the-- the-- the-- the-- the situation, gloated almost, on what was happening to us.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You had very little-- but I must say, there were exception.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We mustn't have it one sided.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were exception, people who did help, who came out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were people, and in my experience, I did have people, who, without any material benefits, helped me along in my survival.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You mean of the war?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the war started.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, you know, I remember the first day of war, September-- beginning of September.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My friend came running to me, she said, isn't it marvelous?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "History will write about us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, she-- poor little thing, she didn't realize what is coming.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't realize, either.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember-- I remember they were stationed in our house, still being the big house, so they need to-- required accommodation.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had wonderful equipment for shaving and, you know, being a child, I used to look on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was one of them, who came to my mother and said, you know, you had your life, but I'm sorry for your child.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, we didn't understand what was coming, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he said, I'm sorry for your daughter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was very short.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We started-- they required people to go to work, men only.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they would just take off people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And by going away, after two weeks, they just took 18 people and shot them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Just the Jewish people, as a goodbye present.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
